<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h4><%= @access_request.name %> has requested access to Capstory.me</h4>
    <p>His or her email is <%= @access_request.email %></p>
		<p>Event Date: <%= @access_request.event_date %></p>
		<p>What is the nature of the request? <%= @access_request.nature_of_request %></p>
		<% if @access_request.industry_pro? %>
			<p>Industry Role: <%= @access_request.industry_role %></p>
		<% end %>
		<p>Questions/Comment: <%= @access_request.questions_comments %></p>
		<p>Partner Code: <%= @access_request.code %></p>
		<p>Go to the <%= link_to "Access Requests Admin Page", @url %> in order to validate their request.</p>
  </body>
</html>